{"tid":579361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人入嚟認識下而家香港本地嘅Hip Hop","createTime":"2018-03-03T14:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T02:32:32.000Z","uid":149118,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90bb212a991edde84e6c2f102eb5f29e610900f1","tid":579361,"uid":149118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"個人認為Bakerie 早班火車呢首歌好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然可能冇乜人識佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我覺得大家一定要聽下呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前嚟過我學校表演不過嗰陣時唔識佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次老佛爺香港站我都有去<br />\n我覺得佢哋應該要紅過啲香港嘅主流歌星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6SvD5pA33Ew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6SvD5pA33Ew&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e5f2d94e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6SvD5pA33Ew</a><br />\n睇埋紀錄片了解下佢地<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6nsaz4MoPJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6nsaz4MoPJA&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e6f34ae2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6nsaz4MoPJA</a><br />\n佢哋其他歌都好正 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2uMsrsMeGUE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2uMsrsMeGUE&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7b792620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2uMsrsMeGUE</a><br />\n當然仲有刀哥呢首<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VJIM8y9dJNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVJIM8y9dJNs&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=45243e92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VJIM8y9dJNs</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋大家可以聽下米奇老味同埋米奇老味嘅奶油包d歌<br />\n個人最鐘意呢首<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pxmfaJsKibI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpxmfaJsKibI&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=13825780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pxmfaJsKibI</a><br />\n奶油包<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iBE4eRbbcVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiBE4eRbbcVE&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=36a95433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iBE4eRbbcVE</a><br />\n奶油包 freestyle <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KWGK9YrLWBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKWGK9YrLWBg&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5d5c6a0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KWGK9YrLWBg</a><br />\n<br />\nYoung queenz  個人認為呢首叫ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F2pErtCrj5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF2pErtCrj5g&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e3688585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F2pErtCrj5g</a><br />\n希望大家可以支持下香港hip hop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183642f1669d564ff85fc245f4836cbf8b1ccb67","tid":579361,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"香港 不了"},{"pid":"cc8c99fa26ab9e58bf5a6c6148a052b99cbab912","tid":579361,"uid":149118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:05:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5d9df9767bf29dc5a3bab99e8fcbf440eacaf20","tid":579361,"uid":149118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bef2313d8b3d172460482e549721f5b36b6dc371","tid":579361,"uid":149118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018